content.source_1: Ogden Township, Champaign County, Illinois Ogden Township is a township in Champaign County, Illinois, USA. As of the 2010 census, its population was 1,680 and it contained 677 housing units. Ogden Township was formed from a portion of South Homer Township on an unknown date. Ogden is parts of Townships 19 and 20 North, Range 11 East of the Third Principal Meridian and part of Range 14 West of the Second Principal Meridian.
